Attribute Name: TOTAL_ON_US_CHECK_ACCEPTS

Related CTE(s):
FQ_BASE, BASE_SUM1

Source Fields Used:
- AGGREGATOR_INDICATOR
- PRE_APPROVED_INDICATOR
- QUOTE_DECISION
- LINKED_APPLICATION_IDENTIFIER

Technical Transformation Summary:
Calculated as the count of records where QUOTE_DECISION = 'Accept', using conditional logic to identify records belonging to the On-us eligibility stage. Filtering includes combinations of aggregator indicator, pre-approved flag, and linked application identifier.

Business Logic:
Represents the number of records that reached the On-us eligibility stage and received an “Accept” decision outcome.

Journey Stage:
Stage 2 – On-us Eligibility Check (Second Check)

Assumptions / Open Questions:
